      <title>IEA说，随着OPEC+增强供应，贸易战侵蚀了石油需求。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/trade-war-threatens-oil-demand-as-opec-boosts-supply-iea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源机构说，全球石油需求来自欧佩克+正在恢复产出的同时，贸易战争不断升级，威胁要加深供应盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/trade-war-threatens-oil-demand-as-opec-boosts-supply-iea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEA说，俄罗斯石油出口几乎完好无损，但价格受到打击。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/russian-oil-exports-almost-intact-but-prices-take-hit-iea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国际能源局称，在实施最新一轮制裁之后，俄罗斯石油出口在2月较低，但价格折扣却限制了收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/russian-oil-exports-almost-intact-but-prices-take-hit-iea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
